<div class='form-auth__wrapper'>
  <form class='form-auth' action='submit'>
    <h1 class='form-auth__title'>Авторизация</h1>
    <div class='form-auth__input'>
      <label for='form-auth-email'>
        <div class='form-auth__input_label'>
          <span>Email</span>
          <svg
            class='form-auth__email-note_icon'
            width='16'
            height='16'
            viewBox='0 0 16 16'
            fill='none'
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
          >
            <path
              d='M8.66667 10.6667H8V8H7.33333M8 5.33333H8.00667M14 8C14 11.3137 11.3137 14 8 14C4.68629 14 2 11.3137 2 8C2 4.68629 4.68629 2 8 2C11.3137 2 14 4.68629 14 8Z'
              stroke='white'
              stroke-width='2'
              stroke-linecap='round'
              stroke-linejoin='round'
            />
          </svg>
          <div class='note auth__email_note'>
            Укажите корректный
            <br />почтовый адрес
          </div>
        </div>

        <input
          name='form-auth-email'
          placeholder='Введите e-mail'
          class='input form-auth__input_field'
          id='form-auth-email'
          type='email'
        />
        <span class='form-auth__input_error' id='form-auth-email-error'></span>

      </label>
    </div>
    <div class='form-auth__input'>
      <label for='form-auth-password'>
        <div class='form-auth__input_label'>
          <span>Пароль</span>
          <svg
            class='form-auth__password-note_icon'
            width='16'
            height='16'
            viewBox='0 0 16 16'
            fill='none'
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
          >
            <path
              d='M8.66667 10.6667H8V8H7.33333M8 5.33333H8.00667M14 8C14 11.3137 11.3137 14 8 14C4.68629 14 2 11.3137 2 8C2 4.68629 4.68629 2 8 2C11.3137 2 14 4.68629 14 8Z'
              stroke='white'
              stroke-width='2'
              stroke-linecap='round'
              stroke-linejoin='round'
            />
          </svg>
          <div class='note auth__password_note'>
            Пароль должен содержать:
            <br />– 8-24 символов;
            <br />– Хотя бы одну цифру;
          </div>
        </div>
        <input
          name='form-auth-password'
          placeholder='Введите пароль'
          class='input form-auth__input_field'
          id='form-auth-password'
          type='password'
        />
        <span
          class='form-auth__input_error'
          id='form-auth-password-error'
        ></span>
      </label>
    </div>
    <div class='form-auth__submit'>
      <button
        class='button form-auth__submit_button'
        id='form-auth-btn'
      >Войти</button>
      <span id='auth-error' class='auth-error'></span>

    </div>
  </form>
  <div class='form-auth__footer'>
    <span class='form-auth__footer_message'>У Вас нет аккаунта?
      <a
        class='form-auth__footer_message_link'
        id='form-auth-reg-link'
        href=''
      >Зарегистрируйтесь</a>
    </span>
  </div>
</div>